question_en: Which temple was built during the reign of Maharaja Jagatprakash?

explanation_en: The Birla Mandir, also known as the Laxmi Narayan Temple, was built in Jaipur during the reign of Maharaja Sawai Jai Singh II. It marks his dedication to Lord Vishnu.
